        "action": "Allow over 21s with a driving licence to ride up to 125cc motorbike without CBT",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We want the Government to implement licensing laws for motorbikes similar to those in Portugal, and allow people aged 21 and over with a full car driving licence to ride motorbikes up to 125cc without talking compulsory basic training (CBT).",
